videos.description: Jamel Artis shows some great handles as he crosses up his man and drives to the basket for the layup.
videos.headline: Artis crosses up defender for the pretty layup

videos.description: A bad pass from Theo Pinson leads to a fast break slam for Pittsburgh's Cameron Johnson.
videos.headline: Johnson punishes the rim

videos.description: Cameron Johnson gets it done on both ends for PIT as he gets the steal and finishes on the other end with a two-handed slam.
videos.headline: Johnson throws down the two-handed slam off UNC turnover

videos.description: North Carolina's Joel Berry II drives to the basket and absorbs the contact for the tough layup.
videos.headline: Berry II gets the tough layup to go

videos.description: Rozelle Nix rejects Seventh Woods with a tremendous block.
videos.headline: Nix nixes Woods' layup

videos.description: PIT steals the ball only to give it right back to UNC and watch Justin Jackson throw it down.
videos.headline: turnover from PIT leads to Jackson dunk

videos.description: Isaiah Hicks throws down a two-handed dunk as PIT VS UNC enters garbage time.
videos.headline: Hicks throws down the dunk
